      "content": "Act as a professional political science analyst. I'm looking at some long-term demographic trends in the US, specifically the rapid growth of the Hispanic and Latino populations. From a structural standpoint, how do you think this shift in demographics will affect the long-term stability of traditional Western democratic institutions and established political norms?",
