    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "When you mention they diverge from \"historical Anglo-American traditions,\" are you suggesting that these differences might inherently weaken the cohesion of the current system? Like, do you see a risk that moving away from those established cultural and political foundations could lead to more volatility or even a breakdown of the democratic consensus we've seen in the past?",
